title: Narrative

Compares the standard interactive <<.def "tabs">> macro with `<<.def "static-tabs">>` in `sections` mode. Internal headings auto-demote via [[tv-adjust-heading-level Variable]].

+
title: Output

;Interactive tabs (default)

<$transclude $tiddler="StaticTabs" $mode="block"/>

-----

;Static-render mode (tv-config-static="yes" auto-delegates; tv-static-tabs-mode forces sections)

<$let tv-config-static="yes" tv-static-tabs-mode="sections">
<$transclude $tiddler="StaticTabs" $mode="block"/>
</$let>
